what_worked: Applied or_to_union, date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate, prefetch_fact_join achieving 53.11x speedup
why_it_worked: Converting OR to UNION ALL lets optimizer choose independent index paths per branch; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
